
  Welcome to the git repository of the RTL/BIDI/Hebrew Moodle project

All files in this repository are palced in the same directory structure of the
original ("vanila") Moodle development tree. ie. cvs.moodle.org
so you can allways sync it directly to your local copy of Moodle

as Admin user, do not forget to navigate to the Site Menu: Admin -> Notification
link, after each pull from this git repository to have the new changes apply
to your local Moodle install.

The Moodle project development wiki : wiki.moodle.org